Invocation Name: hockey team
des:
**Updated for this season and now has the Golden Knights**

This skill will return the last five plays in a live hockey game. If there is a live game on today, you will be informed when it starts in Pacific military time. 

To correctly use the skill invoke it using Hockey team and ask for the Team name you would like.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
